                            Summary on Grant Application Form</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td colspan="6" class="DetailValue" style="padding:5px;">
                        <span id="lblAbstract">To procure copper isotopes which are essential to make a neutron diffraction experiment on the generic chalcohalide glass (Sb2Se3)0.4(Cul)0.6 that has been awarded beam-time at the ISIS facility. The object is to measure the Cu-Cu partial structure factor and related difference functions to provide unique and unambiguous information on the microscopic structure of this material which has good IR characteristics.</span>
                        </td>
		</tr>
